      <title>援助组织称尼日利亚食品价格飙升导致营养不良率飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/malnutrition-soars-amid-nigeria-food-cost-spike-doctors-without-borders-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据非营利组织无国界医生组织称，尼日利亚正面临生活成本危机，营养不良现象日益严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/malnutrition-soars-amid-nigeria-food-cost-spike-doctors-without-borders-says</guid>
