      <title>沙米玛·贝古姆在最高法院挑战取消公民身份的最终失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-07/shamima-begum-loses-final-bid-to-challenge-citizenship-removal-at-supreme-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官裁定，沙米玛·贝古姆不得向最高法院质疑取消其英国国籍的决定。]]></description>
